{"tid":2108190,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"777永續放大量強国隱形武肺病者，香港人走唔到","createTime":"2020-07-14T11:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T15:20:42.000Z","uid":76310,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1159cc6d8aa71cf2f641189a5b15efc04f11d8e","tid":2108190,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"當外國人見到香港大爆發<br />\n就算想收香港人，都害怕武漢肺炎而唔敢<br />\n強国其實仲有大把確診和隱形武肺病者，令佢地免檢，就可以無止境放強国人黎感染香港人<br />\n好似放大量喪屍來傳染病毒咁，一定大把人中<br />\n<br />\n咁樣，香港永續大爆發武漢肺炎，香港人都唔洗旨意走同移民<br />\n等同大鎖港咁，但一切都好自然，外國政府和國際社會都無辦法<br />\n<br />\n大家準備好永續武漢肺炎大爆發未"},{"pid":"c560e0285d839a0359768670c44dad7ae6c1b3fb","tid":2108190,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a109b79605109de4d3a5f15b5ea6f50d24d5f67a","tid":2108190,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a139dcb9bbeaa693d4f49a3af42f4a38f31a8e","tid":2108190,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"日日沖關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a42835e0125b4e620f2921f8bab9024858edb2","tid":2108190,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"777害香港人之心不死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5261dff49fc5cbe2af472d50478704ec510ae3","tid":2108190,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202